Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:50.58,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}那所無法傳達　光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:54.54,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在如此的天地裡　在這樣的世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.13,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}浮生若夢　回眸幾何
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:08.72,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\blur4}你所製作的　玻璃飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:12.44,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\blur4}指尖一觸　寸心如割
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:16.69,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}必不可少的　不再所需的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.69,0:02:19.51,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}至始至終　覆水難收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.07,0:02:24.37,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛　僅需一滴　臉頰便能浸潤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:27.29,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}心如刀絞　雨恨雲愁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:32.70,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我還是對你　一無所知啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:36.75,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那些落淚　就此止泣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:40.55,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}多想與你　歡聲笑語
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:44.89,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如此憧憬　如此嚮往　想像便形成力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:48.75,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就能改變當下　於晴空翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:53.03,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一起出發吧　窗外的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.94,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}攜手與你共賞春秋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.50,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}黑雲已散　風光日霽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.50,0:03:02.08,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨後鏡花水月　依舊彩虹色映
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:08.70,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}雨過天晴的你　眼眸自知物理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:11.83,Yuri004-OP-CHT,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}不過我想讓你　所尋自己而已
